<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=9821900176904></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9821900176904><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=7&mid=9821900176904>RE: AC for Clerics?</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Feb 14th 5:33 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would suggest you start doing the Cleric armor quests.  The boots are relatively easy.  You can pick the ingot and icon up in Kithicor during the day and all you need is levitate :)  Do start thinking of items with wisdom, because your usefullness to a group increasingly continue to depend on your spells.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
