	   <tr><td colspan=2>im considering starting a cleric but first i must decide on a race im after a really holy,spell casting,intelligent,noble,non evil race and i need to know what spells you can get and at what levels you can get them and what offensive spells do clerics have ???????<br><br>thank you<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
