	   <tr><td colspan=2>it is the Regent Symbol of Innoruuk. Available only to Clerics and Shamans of the Teir'Dal, Troll  and Ogres.   There are two other symbols : The Intiate's and the Disciple's you need to get before you can get the Regent's.  The Regent symbol is ac 7 wis +3 int +2 +15 mana and cast clinging darkness. A very fitting neckpiece for the Darker Clerics out there.<br><br><br>      Zahgurim D'Veldrin - Tarew Marr<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
