	   <tr><td colspan=2>As a player who's primary character is a dark elf cleric, I have to say, that playing a dark elf cleric has been a great experience.   Nothing like preaching to the goodie goodies about thier falling to innoruuk's ploy by actually hating us.  To hear the stammered replies of human clerics who claim to worship Errolisi Marr after they say something spiteful about your race, and you thank them for thier spite from yourself and Innoruuk.  The cold unfeeling glare as someone you dilike runs to you begging for a heal and you turn your back, or deny them a ress because they've been rude, or inconsiderate to you, is totally RP.  It's great.  Have fun with it.  From a stat perspective, we lack in the str dept, but we can get a pretty good starting wis, which is always nice for mana.  Besides, beinga plate class, just about everyone will agree that plate looks best on DEs.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
