	   <tr><td colspan=2>How do you know if you are a high enough skill to make armor?  I tried to make banded armor yesterday and it didn't work.  I'm pretty sure i had enough training on smithing in order to make banded armor.  I have a question about making it.  The ingredients are one sheet metal, one water flask, and then the mold of the piece of armor you want to make.  Well i was going to make it but i couldn't find the pattern.  So i tried to make chainmail.  My question is do you need a pattern for the kind of armor your going to make such as steel, banded, chainmail, etc.?  If so where can i find the pattern for the banded armor?  I am in Qeynos and i'm not sure if there is a place in Qeynos that i can buy it at.  Also, for when i can make it what are the ingredients to make steel and what training do you have to have?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
